{"tid":2285114,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實CNN和白兵真係做撚緊同一樣既野","createTime":"2020-11-13T23:50:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-03T08:20:38.000Z","uid":31637,"like":5,"dislike":62,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"2a3d68c7fcd9c0665e957c4a12437df37b7f6c35","tid":2285114,"uid":31637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T23:50:41.000Z","msg":"就係一年365日都以邪教方式營運,向佢D聽眾/觀眾洗腦,唱衰政敵<br />\n吹撚到真。本土派/美國民主黨係該國唯一希望<br />\n但其實２個都係該國最撚冇能既果班人<br />\n<br />\n真。本土派：<br />\n無能力推翻政權<br />\n無能力勾結外國勢力<br />\n對泛民就兇恨，對共產黨就碌撚<br />\n<br />\n美國民主黨：<br />\n有能力但無膽激嬲共產黨<br />\n有能力但無膽出兵打北韓<br />\n對共和黨就兇恨，對共產黨就碌撚"},{"pid":"ef53f964b3ebae9074bacdcabeead431757ffc33","tid":2285114,"uid":31637,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T23:57:09.000Z","msg":"泛民＝落場踢波踢到成ＰＡＴ屎咁既球員<br />\n白兵與他的真本土派們＝屌鳩球員踢波踢到成ＰＡＴ屎咁既觀眾席觀眾<br />\n<br />\n真本土派係唯一希望呀，咁求撚其係觀眾席搵１２個觀眾落場踢都可以拎世界盃／歐冠杯啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cee5741050cef1fa55d4fe19f9d878138b554dfb","tid":2285114,"uid":6604,"like":8,"dislike":12,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T23:58:07.000Z","msg":"2020年白兵 = 2014年嘅熱狗"},{"pid":"a0330fce958ee1ff63c597b4ee19013ffe325792","tid":2285114,"uid":31637,"like":4,"dislike":7,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"cee5741050cef1fa55d4fe19f9d878138b554dfb","tid":2285114,"uid":6604,"like":8,"dislike":12,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T23:58:07.000Z","msg":"2020年白兵 = 2014年嘅熱狗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T23:59:55.000Z","msg":"模式根撚本１００００００％一鳩樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2d91d50311da1540ad9042ca90e9839abd5ba84","tid":2285114,"uid":43468,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T09:05:10.000Z","msg":"講白兵支持美國民主黨？你係假膠？"},{"pid":"bac5ec15770f002b71fd1533583c1473cc12bbc1","tid":2285114,"uid":196359,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T09:08:06.000Z","msg":"白兵撐共和黨架wo，c兄"},{"pid":"740102c87e8be77e266c160ee7